Madagascar Faces Shortage of 100,000 Tons of Rice, Midi Reports

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-08-30T12:24:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-30/madagascar-faces-shortage-of-100-000-tons-of-rice-midi-reports.html
Madagascar faces a shortage of
100,000 metric tons of rice,  Midi Madagasikara said , without
saying where it obtained the information.  The government will import to satisfy local demand, the
Antananarivo-based newspaper said on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
